# Project Structure

## Directory Structure (Full-Stack Monorepo)

```
project_root/
├── backend/              # Backend service (Python or TypeScript)
│   ├── src/
│   │   ├── domain/       # Core business logic (no external deps)
│   │   ├── application/  # Use cases, agents, workflows
│   │   ├── infrastructure/ # External dependencies (LLMs, DBs, APIs)
│   │   └── api/          # API layer (REST/GraphQL)
│   ├── tests/            # Test suite
│   └── configs/          # Configs, prompts
├── frontend/             # Frontend application
│   ├── src/
│   │   ├── components/   # UI components
│   │   ├── pages/        # Page components
│   │   ├── services/     # API client services
│   │   ├── store/        # State management
│   │   └── types/        # TypeScript types
│   └── tests/
├── shared/               # Shared code
│   ├── types/            # Shared TypeScript types
│   └── schemas/          # Shared validation schemas (Zod)
└── docs/                 # Documentation
```

## Dependency Rules

### Backend Layers
```
domain/          → No dependencies (pure logic)
application/     → domain/ only
infrastructure/  → domain/, application/ (implements interfaces)
api/            → application/, infrastructure/
```

### Cross-Layer
```
shared/         → No dependencies on backend/ or frontend/
backend/        → Can import from shared/
frontend/       → Can import from shared/
```

## Module Organization

- **Domain**: Pure business logic, no external dependencies
- **Application**: Orchestrates domain logic, contains LangChain/LangGraph workflows
- **Infrastructure**: Implements interfaces, handles external systems
- **API**: Thin layer translating HTTP to application calls
- **Frontend**: Component-based, type-safe API clients

## File Naming

- **Modules**: `snake_case.py` (Python) or `camelCase.ts` (TypeScript)
- **Classes**: `PascalCase`
- **Functions/Variables**: `snake_case` (Python) or `camelCase` (TypeScript)
- **Constants**: `UPPER_SNAKE_CASE`

## Module Size

- **Files**: Max 300 lines (ideally <200)
- **Functions**: Max 50 lines (ideally <20)
- **Classes**: Max 500 lines (ideally <200)
